### Listar todas as colmeias (paginado)
GET http://localhost:8080/hives?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

### Buscar colmeia por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/hives/1
Accept: application/json

### Criar nova colmeia
POST http://localhost:8080/hives
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "beeSpecies": "Apis mellifera",
  "lastHarvest": "2025-09-01",
  "installationDate": "2025-06-10",
  "status": "HEALTHY",
  "nickname": "Colmeia Azul",
  "population": 12000,
  "production": 15.7,
  "coordinates": "-25.4284,-49.2733",
  "inspectionNote": 9,
  "propertyId": 1,
  "deviceId": 3
}

### Atualizar colmeia existente
PUT http://localhost:8080/hives/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "beeSpecies": "Apis mellifera",
  "lastHarvest": "2025-09-10",
  "installationDate": "2025-06-10",
  "status": "INACTIVE",
  "nickname": "Colmeia Revisada",
  "population": 11000,
  "production": 14.2,
  "coordinates": "-25.4284,-49.2733",
  "inspectionNote": 8,
  "propertyId": 1,
  "deviceId": 2
}

### Deletar colmeia
DELETE http://localhost:8080/hives/1
Accept: application/json
